descriptionHtml:
The iCount time app invites you to translate your working time into money by tracking your work day - whether it's daily attendance or a specific project - and translating it into accurate invoices to your clients.
In addition, the Time application gives you a complete control over the attendance management of your employees - approval of days off and days of absence, a monthly attendance report and receiving notifications every time they start or end their working day.

Over 60,000 business owners have chosen us. And you? No need to decide now, there's a 45-day free trial.
